item.title: Josh add a quote by Ayn Rand
item.description: "A government is the most dangerous threat to man's rights: it holds a legal monopoly on the use of physical force against legally disarmed victims." -- Ayn Rand

item.title: Josh add a quote by Ayn Rand
item.description: "So you think that money is the root of all evil. Have you ever asked what is the root of all money?" -- Ayn Rand

item.title: Josh add a quote by Ayn Rand
item.description: "The smallest minority on earth is the individual. Those who deny individual rights cannot claim to be defenders of minorities." -- Ayn Rand

item.title: Josh add a quote by Ayn Rand
item.description: "I swear by my life and my love of it that I will never live for the sake of another man, nor ask another man to live for mine." -- Ayn Rand

item.title: Josh add a quote by Ayn Rand
item.description: "Do not ever say that the desire to "do good" by force is a good motive. Neither power-lust nor stupidity are good motives." -- Ayn Rand

item.title: Josh add a quote by Mark Twain
item.description: "If you tell the truth, you don't have to remember anything." -- Mark Twain

item.title: Josh add a quote by Dr. Seuss
item.description: "Don't cry because it's over, smile because it happened." -- Dr. Seuss

item.title: Josh add a quote by Theodore Roosevelt
item.description: "Do what you can, with what you have, where you are." -- Theodore Roosevelt

item.title: Josh add a quote by Henry Ford
item.description: "Whether you think you can, or you think you can't--you're right." -- Henry Ford

item.title: Josh add a quote by Mark Twain
item.description: "Keep away from people who try to belittle your ambitions. Small people always do that, but the really great make you feel that you, too, can become great." -- Mark Twain

item.title: Josh add a quote by Dr. Seuss
item.description: "The more that you read, the more things you will know. The more that you learn, the more places you'll go." -- Dr. Seuss

item.title: Josh add a quote by Confucious
item.description: "Choose a job you love, and you will never have to work a day in your life." -- Confucious
